The UN Human Rights Council's 50th session kicks off in Geneva on June 13, ahead of which, the U.S. again falsely accused China of human rights violations. But in fact, the deep-rooted racism and gun violence in the U.S. have already exposed its abysmal human rights records and revealed to the world its true colors – a fake human rights defender, but a true human rights destroyer! (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)